data.description: Come see this beautiful Beazer built home. This home is only 3 years young and has too many features to list. From the welcoming front porch, all the way to your covered back patio, you need to come see this home Today! Your foyer leads into your open kitchen and living room combo. On the right side you will find your MUD room and your private utility room. Enjoy all the windows, high ceilings and natural lighting in this one story home. Your primary room is attached to your grand bathroom with standup shower and walk-in closet. The other rooms include 2 addtional bedrooms, a gameroom/flex space and study area. You also have a covered back patio with and extended porch for those Spring/Summer gatherings. Schedule to see this home Today!
